t rest is altogether </div><div class="t m42a x16 h28 y64c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">future, and that the saints have not yet entered into </div><div class="t m758 x16 h28 y64d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it. </div><div class="t m5 x14 h28 y64d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m759 x29 h28 y64e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Yet some claim that it is a present blessing, but </div><div class="t m75a x16 h28 y64f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">contrary to the whole tenor of the apostle&apos;s argument. </div><div class="t m4a3 x16 h28 y650 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lange&apos;s Commentari; says: &quot;From the nature of </div><div class="t m12a x16 h28 y651 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the rest of God it frjllows that for the people of God, </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
